00:35:06.079 --> 00:35:07.870
FREDERICK "SHAD" ROWE:
Compared to T. Rowe?

00:35:07.870 --> 00:35:08.720
PRANESH SRINIVASAN:
T. Rowe, yeah.

00:35:08.720 --> 00:35:09.780
FREDERICK "SHAD" ROWE: I
