00:36:28.680 --> 00:36:30.730
guy in the world for a while.

00:36:30.730 --> 00:36:34.590
And what did he do-- he just
had an obsession with money

00:36:34.590 --> 00:36:37.490
and never spent it,
and just compounded,

00:36:37.490 --> 00:36:39.306
compounded, compounded.

00:36:39.306 --> 00:36:44.520
AUDIENCE: I always wonder
about nonprofit investments.

00:36:44.520 --> 00:36:47.850
And when I think of
Buffett or Gates and a lot

00:36:47.850 --> 00:36:51.090
of philanthropic
investments, you

00:36:51.090 --> 00:36:53.610
know-- is it in the
context of philanthropy

00:36:53.610 --> 00:36:54.600
versus giving away.

00:36:54.600 --> 00:36:57.630
What's this actual investment
