just charging more every year.

00:37:41.820 --> 00:37:43.194
And it's become
too big a burden.

00:37:45.940 --> 00:37:49.460
Not to complain about it, but
yeah, I think it's an issue.

00:37:49.460 --> 00:37:52.580
You know, you don't want
to die with all your money.

00:37:52.580 --> 00:37:55.790
And you'd rather have you
decide what to do with it

00:37:55.790 --> 00:37:57.950
than let someone else
decide what to do with it.

00:37:57.950 --> 00:37:58.910
Certainly.

00:37:58.910 --> 00:38:02.590
any one is going to do better
than the government, probably.

00:38:02.590 --> 00:38:05.320
But I think it's a big issue.

00:38:05.320 --> 00:38:08.250
We don't live forever,
because we all think we will.

