00:39:08.685 --> 00:39:09.570
FREDERICK "SHAD" ROWE:
That's very hard to do.

00:39:09.570 --> 00:39:11.690
AUDIENCE: --worse case--
end up in stage two, but--

00:39:11.690 --> 00:39:12.120
FREDERICK "SHAD"
ROWE: Because they're

00:39:12.120 --> 00:39:14.540
successful in stage one,
and that leads to problems.

00:39:14.540 --> 00:39:15.456
Just like with people.

00:39:15.456 --> 00:39:18.630
It's just exactly like a person.

00:39:18.630 --> 00:39:24.880
And you know, at some point,
the company is successful,

00:39:24.880 --> 00:39:26.470
and it wants to
do something else.

00:39:26.470 --> 00:39:28.553
And the individual wants
to do something else that

00:39:28.553 --> 00:39:30.480
didn't make them the
money in the first place.

00:39:30.480 --> 00:39:32.530
And this is exactly
the same thing.

00:39:32.530 --> 00:39:34.960
So you want to make enough
money so that your comfortable

00:39:34.960 --> 00:39:37.293
and you get your needs taken
care of, but that's enough,

00:39:37.293 --> 00:39:41.580
probably, unless it becomes
a game or an obsession.

00:39:41.580 --> 00:39:43.500
But you're right, exactly.

00:39:43.500 --> 00:39:46.150
It is the same thing
as with a person.

